<SiteLayout title="Use cases | Zentio" lang="en">
  <h1>Use cases</h1>
  <p>Automation applied to the routines that slow down day-to-day operations.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Operations: routing, checklists, approvals</li>
    <li>Finance: reconciliation, billing, notifications</li>
    <li>Sales: lead distribution, CRM updates, follow-ups</li>
    <li>Support: triage, SLA, escalation</li>
    <li>HR/Backoffice: onboarding, internal requests</li>
    <li>Compliance: logs, validations, audit trails</li>
  </ul>
</SiteLayout>
